> [!NOTE]
> Supported request keys:
>
> | `.` Variables | `@` Body | `#` Headers |
> | ------------- | -------- | ----------- |
> | +{{{- if includes .args "variables" -}}}✅+{{{- else -}}}❌+{{{- end -}}}
    | +{{{- if includes .args "body" -}}}✅+{{{- else -}}}❌+{{{- end -}}}
    | +{{{- if includes .args "headers" -}}}✅+{{{- else -}}}❌+{{{- end -}}} |
